---
title: Coconutty Fish Curry with Green Beans
description: Mild, coconutty and on the table in just 30 minutes, Chef Andre’s crowd-pleasing fish curry is the perfect midweek recipe. Tilapia fillets are cooked in a velvety sauce seasoned with our mild Indian spice blend and packed with fresh veg, before being served with steamed jasmine rice and topped with toasted desiccated coconut. You next curry night shouldn’t be without this special recipe.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/coconutty-fish-curry-670fc924-965ce195.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/coconutty-fish-curry-5bb72f6630006c4ea1772392-009069e8.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/coconutty-fish-curry-5bb72f6630006c4ea1772392
servings: 2
cuisine: Indonesian
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
nutrition:
  calories: 575 kcal
